title: Akinyele - Vagina Diner (Nodzilla5)
description:
I swiped this Gem though ebay. The CD is currently out of print, but the tracks are a part of hip hop history.  Track singles such as "The Bomb" and "Worldwide" graced underground DJ Mix Tapes in NJ and NY through 93 and 94.  I clearly remember Double R lacing one of his tapes with a few of Ak&#039;s tracks.  I miss the good old days!

PS - My Boy Eto crashed my 87 Celica in Brooklyn listening to Worldwide!
